sentences.sentence: Ninety percent of Qatari citizens live in Doha.
The Qatari riyal (currency code QAR) is the official currency of Qatar.
sentences.translation: 卡塔尔亚尔(货币代码QAR)是卡塔尔的官方货币。

sentences.sentence: Orry, a Qatari oryx , is the Official Mascot of the Doha Asian Games 2006.
sentences.translation: 第15届亚运会吉祥物是一只名叫“奥利”(Orry)的卡塔尔羚羊。
